info.title: Simple message logger
info.description:
This is a message logger that loggs messages.
It saves them in '{bot folder}/transcripts/{channel-name}.log'

If this is used for like a ticket bot transcript, its fine, 

BUT

If you are just logging every single message that the bot sees, WITHOUT giving users BOTH a heads up, and a way to opt out, its against TOS.
